<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  [%- PROCESS config.tt -%]
  [%- title = "Utility tools" -%]  
  [%- INCLUDE header.tt
  desc="Utility tools is a set of utils to manage rules."
  keywords="Tools, rules, utils, atomic-head, singlepiece-head,
  singlepiece, atomic rule, datalog+"
  -%]<html>
  
  <body>

    <!-- HEADER -->
    <div id="header_wrap" class="outer">
        <header class="inner">
          <h1 id="project_title">[% title %]</h1>
        </header>
        [%- INCLUDE nav.tt -%]
    </div>

    [%- INCLUDE downloads_sub_menu.tt -%]

    <!-- MAIN CONTENT -->
    <div id="main_content_wrap" class="outer">
      <section id="main_content" class="inner">

        <p>The utility-tools program is a set of utilities to manage
          rules. It currently has three features:</p>
        <dl>
          <dt>atomic-head</dt><dd>transform a rule set into a set
          of atomic-head rules.</dd>
          <dt>singlepiece-head</dt><dd>transform a rule set into a
          set of single-piece head rules.</dd>
          <dt>labeler</dt><dd>add labels to each rule:
              <ul>
          <li><strong>CI</strong>: Concept Inclusion - <em>A(x) -> B(x)</em></li>
          <li><strong>RI</strong>: Role Inclusion - <em>p(x,y) -> r(x,y)</em></li>
          <li><strong>Inv</strong>: Inverse Role - <em>p(x,y) -> r(y,x)</em></li>
          <li><strong>Dom</strong>: Domain - <em> p(x,y) -> A(x)</em></li>
          <li><strong>Rng</strong>: Range - <em>p(x,y) -> A(y)</em></li>
          <li><strong>MR</strong>: Mandatory Role - <em>A(x) -> p(x,y)</em></li>
          <li><strong>IMR</strong>: Inverse Mandatory Role - <em>A(y) -> p(x,y)</em></li>
          <li><strong>ERC</strong>: Existential quantification in rule
            heads - <em>A(x) -> p(x,y), B(y)</em></li>
          <li><strong>IERC</strong>: ERC with Inverse role - <em>A(x) -> p(y,x), B(y)</em></li>
          <li><strong>Trans</strong>: Transitivity - <em>p(x,y),p(y,z) -> p(x,z)</em></li>
          <li><strong>RC</strong>: Role Composition - <em> p(x,y),r(y,z) -> s(x,z)</em></li>
          <li><strong>Func</strong>: Functional dependency - <em> BODY -> x = y</em></li>
          <li><strong>DC</strong>: Disjoint Concept - <em>! A(x), B(x)</em></li>
          <li><strong>DR</strong>: Disjoint Role - <em>!
              p(x,y),r(x,y)</em></li>
          <li><strong>NC</strong>: Negative Constraint - <em> ! BODY </em></li>
        </ul>
          </dd>
        </dl>
        
        <h2>Getting started</h2>
           
        <ul>
            <li>Download <a href="./dl/utility-tools-1.0.0.jar">utility-tools</a></li>
            <li>Download <a href="./dl/example1.dlp">example1.dlp</a></li>
        </ul>

        <h3> Compute atomic head rules </h3>

        <code>java -jar utility-tools-*.jar -a < ./example1.dlp </code>
     

        <h3> Compute single-piece head rules </h3>

        <code>java -jar utility-tools-*.jar -p < ./example1.dlp </code>
   

        <h3> Label rules </h3>
        
        <code>java -jar utility-tools-*.jar -l < ./example1.dlp</code>
        
      </section>
    </div>

  [%- INCLUDE footer.tt -%]

  </body>
</html>
